			  	Ok, j0ker, this is how you could contain antimatter:<br />
1. Create Antimatter in a super collider.<br />
2. Extract antimatter in an airtight container.  The container would have magnets on it, suspending the antimatter in the center of the container.<br />
3. Place antimatter container in a place where power can be supplied to the magnets to keep them working.<br />
<br />
This is what CERN has been doing to contain antimatter.  If you don't believe me, look it up.  Antimatter exists!<br />
